com.robopupu.api.feature

Interface FeatureContainer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    FeatureTransitionManager
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    FeatureContainerProvider
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FeatureContainerAdapter, PluginActivity, PluginCompatActivity

    public interface FeatureContainer
extends FeatureTransitionManager
    FeatureContainer extends FeatureTransitionManager to define an interface for objects that can be used to show FeatureCompatFragments. Typically a such object is an Activity.
